- json plugin:
    # !json create <name> <url> <extract1> <extract2> ... <extractN>
    # !json del <name>
    # !json [show] <name>

- internationalization 
  - Config.language = "en_US"
  - "strings-dir" /strings/<lang> for each dir
  - /strings/default is a link to default lang
  - /strings/<lang>/plugin-<pluginname>.data
  - /strings/<lang>/general.data
  - foo.data contains one line for each string-id, like this:
    myhello = Hello guys this is an english text
  - provide global function _(str_id) which returns the appropriate string for the global set language

